{"tid":1391146,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警員家屬成立組織「警員親屬連線」促設獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-07-31T10:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T08:25:53.000Z","uid":35790,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5f913c6b31580490be3858b7778dec1420b423ba","tid":1391146,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:43:48.000Z","msg":"警員家屬成立組織促設獨委會<br />\n<br />\n2019/07/31<br />\n<br />\n有警員家屬成立組織要求成立獨立調查委員會，徹查反修例衝突，希望挽回警隊聲譽，同時調查警隊高層調動人手不當問題。 <br />\n<br />\n六、七月反修例示威，警民衝突場面幾乎每個星期出現。有警務人員親屬認為，政府不積極回應市民訴求，加上警隊高層指揮失當，令前線成為犧牲品。受訪家屬與其他警務人員家屬成立「警員親屬連線」，希望化解僵局，支持成立獨立調查委員會，立場跟多個警察協會相反。 <br />\n<br />\n員佐級協會近期的強硬聲明，她說事前沒問過所有警員，不少前線覺得，這只會令他們被人駡得更厲害，但很多時候都不敢出聲。<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/553758/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E4%BF%83%E8%A8%AD%E7%8D%A8%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F553758%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E4%25BF%2583%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFvvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=5260f4c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F553758%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E4%25BF%2583%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583&h=c1cfb84d\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/553758/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E4%BF%83%E8%A8%AD%E7%8D%A8%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n重組警隊"